<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-slate-800">
  <%= image_tag "background.jpeg", class: "absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top scale-105", alt: "" %>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-slate-950/60 via-slate-950/50 to-slate-950"></div>
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 md:py-20 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-sky-500/40 bg-slate-950/70 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-sky-200 shadow-sm shadow-sky-500/20">
        Previsioni sperimentali probabilistiche dal 2015
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          Previsioni dedicate ai temporali intensi
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-300 max-w-xl">
          PRETEMP fornisce previsioni probabilistiche del rischio di fenomeni temporaleschi intensi
          su scala nazionale, con particolare attenzione alle situazioni potenzialmente pericolose.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <%= link_to "Ultima previsione", forecast_path(@latest_forecast),
            class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sky-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-950 shadow-lg shadow-sky-500/30 hover:bg-sky-400 transition" %>
        <%= link_to "Come funziona la previsione", guida_alle_previsioni_path,
            class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-700 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-100 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 transition" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:pl-8">
      <%= render "forecast_card", forecast: @latest_forecast, variant: :latest %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="storm-divider max-w-6xl mx-auto"></div>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 md:py-12 border-b border-slate-800">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Previsioni recenti</h2>
    <%= link_to "Vai all'archivio", archivio_index_path,
        class: "text-xs font-medium text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200" %>
  </div>
  <div class="grid gap-4 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <% (@latest_forecasts || []).each do |forecast| %>
      <%= render "forecast_card", forecast: forecast %>
    <% end %>
    <% if (@latest_forecasts || []).empty? %>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
        Le previsioni verranno mostrate qui non appena disponibili.
      </p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="storm-divider max-w-6xl mx-auto"></div>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 md:py-12 border-b border-slate-800">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Articoli recenti</h2>
    <%= link_to "Vai al blog", articles_path,
        class: "text-xs font-medium text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200" %>
  </div>
  <div class="grid gap-4 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <% if @latest_articles.present? %>
      <% @latest_articles.each do |article| %>
        <%= render "article_card", article: article %>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">
        Gli articoli verranno mostrati qui non appena disponibili.
      </p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="storm-divider max-w-6xl mx-auto"></div>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 md:py-12">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-4 md:p-6 space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Raccolta dati e osservazioni</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mx-4">
      STORM REPORT è un progetto PRETEMP-METEONETWORK che si pone l'obiettivo di archiviare le segnalazioni relative a temporali forti in Italia. Questi dati risultano molto importanti per studi climatologici, validare previsioni e allenare modelli di machine learning. Dall'estate 2019 PRETEMP collabora con l'European Severe Storms Laboratory (ESSL) inviando le segnalazioni anche all'European Severe Weather Database (ESWD).  Al momento le associazioni e i singoli osservatori che supportano questo progetto sono riportati nella pagina dedicata, chiunque volesse diventare volontario o proporre la collaborazione di associazioni è invitato a scriverci (vedi contatti)!
      Inoltre, PRETEMP classifica i tornado che si verificano in Italia utilizzando la scala International Fujita proposta da ESSL.
      <span class="block mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-white">Come citare l’utilizzo dei dati dello Storm Report:</span>
      De Martin, F., Carlon, N., Pavan, F., Carpentari, S., Giazzi, M., Peressutti, G., Miglietta, M. M., and Davolio, S.: Toward a dedicated warning system of severe storms in Italy: the PRETEMP project, 11th European Conference on Severe Storms, Bucharest, Romania, 8–12 May 2023, ECSS2023-18, <a href="https://doi.org/10.5194/ecss2023-18" class="text-blue-500 underline">https://doi.org/10.5194/ecss2023-18</a>, 2023
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="storm-divider max-w-6xl mx-auto"></div>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 md:py-12 border-b border-slate-800">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Frequenza annua di fenomeni temporaleschi in Italia <br>
      Dati Storm Report 2018-2025</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-2 w-full md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.333%-0.67rem)] flex flex-col items-center justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 text-center font-bold my-2">Frequenza annua di grandinate</p>
      <%= image_tag "hail_Italy_new.png", class: "rounded-xl w-full", alt: "" %>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-2 w-full md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.333%-0.67rem)] flex flex-col items-center justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 text-center font-bold my-2">Frequenza annua di vento forte convettivo</p>
      <%= image_tag "wind_Italy_new.png", class: "rounded-xl w-full", alt: "" %>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-2 w-full md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.333%-0.67rem)] flex flex-col items-center justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 text-center font-bold my-2">Frequenza annua di tornado</p>
      <%= image_tag "tornado_Italy_new.png", class: "rounded-xl w-full", alt: "" %>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-2 w-full md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.333%-0.67rem)] flex flex-col items-center justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 text-center font-bold my-2">Frequenza annua di precipitazioni intense convettive</p>
      <%= image_tag "rain_Italy_new.png", class: "rounded-xl w-full", alt: "" %>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-2 w-full md:w-[calc(50%-0.5rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.333%-0.67rem)] flex flex-col items-center justify-between">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 text-center font-bold my-2">Frequenza annua di trombe marine</p>
      <%= image_tag "trombamarina_Italy_new.png", class: "rounded-xl w-full", alt: "" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="storm-divider max-w-6xl mx-auto"></div>
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 md:py-12 border-b border-slate-800">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Ricerca</h2>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-4 md:p-6 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Grandine</h2>
      <%= image_tag "grandine.png", class: "rounded-xl card-storm-glow w-full max-w-full md:max-w-2/3 mx-auto" %>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        De Martin, F., Manzato, A., Carlon, N., Setvák, M. &amp; Miglietta, M.M. (2025) Dynamic and statistical analysis of giant hail environments in northeast Italy. Quarterly Journal of the Royal Meteorological Society, 151(769), e4945. Available from: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/qj.4945" class="text-blue-500 underline">https://doi.org/10.1002/qj.4945</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-4 md:p-6 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Tornado</h2>
      <%= image_tag "tornado.png", class: "rounded-xl card-storm-glow w-full max-w-full md:max-w-2/3 mx-auto" %>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        De Martin, F., F. Pavan, N. Carlon, G. Cioni, C. Rozoff, V. Poli, S. Carpentari, and M. M. Miglietta, 2025: A Significant Tornado Event near a Dryline Bulge in Northern Italy. Wea. Forecasting, 40, 2293–2315, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1175/WAF-D-25-0071.1" class="text-blue-500 underline">https://doi.org/10.1175/WAF-D-25-0071.1</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/80 p-4 md:p-6 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight section-heading-accent">Downburst</h2>
      <%= image_tag "downburst.png", class: "rounded-xl card-storm-glow w-full max-w-full md:max-w-2/3 mx-auto" %>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        De Martin, F., Miglietta, M.M., Gastaldo, T., Martinazzo, M., Pavan, F., Siena, M. and Di Sabatino, S. (2025), The Bayesian sinking in Porticello: a predictable convective windstorm?. Weather, 80: 365-373. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/wea.7715" class="text-blue-500 underline">https://doi.org/10.1002/wea.7715</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="storm-divider max-w-6xl mx-auto"></div>
